    <section name="Core Tasks">

      <subsection name="Description">

        <p>
        The core tasks provide support for the establish of the Magic
        project model, parameterized filters, build preperation, compilation, 
        unit testing, plugin meta-data generation, and multi-project builds.
        </p>

        <p><i>Example build file:</i></p>

<pre><![CDATA[
<project name="example" 
    xmlns:x="plugin:dpml/magic/dpml-magic-core">
  ....
</project>
]]></pre>

      </subsection>

      <subsection name="Artifact URI"><source>@MAGIC-PLUGIN-URI@</source></subsection>

      <subsection name="Antlib Namespace"><source>plugin:dpml/magic/dpml-magic-core</source></subsection>

    </section>
